name: Mnemonic frames #1 🟥
description:
This is the first piece of the "Mnemonic frames" series.
It's based on the simplified chinese version of BIP39 (https://github.com/bitcoin/bips/blob/master/bip-0039/chinese_simplified.txt).

-- The collection --
🎞 Mnemonic frames 🎞

This collection is based on the 2048 words of the BIP39 standard.
The mnemonic phrase is the key to being your own bank.

Please don't use the pieces of this collection as a base for your own mnemonic phrase, that would not be safe.
